HEADWORD: departing
<hw>departing</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>leaving a starting or stopping
point on a journey; <as>as, <ex>Departing</ex> flights were delayed by
the snowstorm</as>. Opposite of <ant>arriving</ant>.</def>
<mark>[prenominal]</mark>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> outbound, outward, outward-bound.</syn>⟦br⟧
